### Say ###

simple www.forvo.com client

### About ###

say - used to listen pronunciations of words from forvo service.
example of usage:
    $ say table
    $ say just in time

Default language - English, language can be changed by invoking:
    $ say -lng=XXX  (where XXX: language abbreviation)

For example, the following call changes the language to Russian, and all subsequent invocations will be use this language:
    $ say -lng=ru



